{"type":"message","id":"7ba2822c","parentId":"f4e4ffe0","timestamp":"2026-05-14T00:56:26.160Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_rNLc3h8Avj75hsQR6WYkMvIu|fc_094b6994f4566fc6016a051db933048194a5cba49236157c6a","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"───────┬──────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Account  │ Status   │ Notes                                                                                          │\n├──────────┼──────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ default  │ OK       │ token:config · credential available in gateway runtime                                         │\n└──────────┴──────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nAgents\n┌────────────┬────────────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Agent      │ Bootstrap file │ Sessions │ Active   │ Store                                                            │\n├────────────┼────────────────┼──────────┼──────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ main       │ ABSENT         │        1 │ just now │ ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json                   │\n└────────────┴────────────────┴──────────┴──────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nDiagnosis (read-only)\n\nGateway connection details:\n  Gateway target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\n  Source: local loopback\n  Config: /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n  Bind: loopback\n\n✓ Config: /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n✓ Secret diagnostics (0)\n✓ Restart sentinel: none\n! Port 18789\n  Port 18789 is already in use.\n  - pid 404772 root: /usr/bin/node /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/index.js gateway --port 18789 (127.0.0.1:18789)\n  - Gateway already running locally. Stop it (openc