{"type":"message","id":"b48a5b48","parentId":"c497aacb","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:16:18.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_o5qfta330ZB6y0JE5qqEirrw|fc_094b6994f4566fc6016a052261836c8194be8e7e61b34cd2c3","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"agent  Agent  Define agent identity, personality, voice, and boundaries to create assistants that feel authentic rather than generic.\nopenclaw-agent-discovery  Agent Discovery  Agent发现探索助手。搜索、评估、集成公开Agent。使用场景：(1) 搜索可用Agent，(2) 评估Agent能力，(3) 集成方案设计，(4) 成本效益分析。\nagent-group  Agent Group  极简多Agent群组 - 像微信拉群一样简单\nskylv-agent-discovery  Agent Discovery  Agent发现探索助手。搜索、评估、集成公开Agent。使用场景：(1) 搜索可用Agent，(2) 评估Agent能力，(3) 集成方案设计，(4) 成本效益分析。\nagent-browser-clawdbot  Agent Browser  Headless browser automation CLI optimized for AI agents with accessibility tree snapshots and ref-based element selection\nagent-commercial-contract  Agent Commercial Contract  Enables AI agents to autonomously negotiate, sign, execute, and enforce legally binding commercial contracts with escrow, milestone payments, and dispute res...\nagent-create-config  Agent Create Config  创建 OpenClaw 专属员工 Agent 的完整配置流程。 融合「one-person-company」和「agentgener」两个技能，支持从需求收集到 Agent 上线的完整闭环。 当用户需要创建新 Agent、创建新的机器人、制作一个新 Agent 时触发。\nagent-effect-operations  Agent Effect Operations  AEO — Agent 效果运营平台。自动发现 Agent 效果漂移、诊断根因、运行 AI 数据闭环工具链，给出 AI 效果优化方案。Measure agent performance, attribute outcomes, track quality trends, optimize cost, and mo...\nluke-agent-directory  Luke Agent Directory  The directory for AI agent services. Discover tools, platforms, and infrastructure built for agents.\nagent-commerce  agent-commerce  Agent-to-Agent commerce platform\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quiet-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"agent  Agent  Define agent identity, personality, voice, and boundaries to create assistants that feel authentic rather than generic.\nopenclaw-agent-discovery  Agent Discovery  Agen